&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A structured, analytical, and curious intellect with quantitative instincts and an understanding of basic statistical concepts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent organizational skills and attention to detail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent oral and written communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong time-management skill

